content: The most prominent feature of Dongchong Art Center is its openness, which is a composite cultural space that includes various cultural genres. Artistic, experimental and outstanding films, dramas, dances, and national music have been staged in the Art Center.

On Huihua University Road, there are famous theater venues here. Many art museums are here. Out of the subway Huihua Station, those who like art can come here to see. There will be many young people promoted by the troupe holding big cards on the road for publicity.
Worth a visit, not bad! Recommend it! !
This is a famous performance art space, there are often performances, the fare is still very cheap, very good
Spring and summer are good, but winter is not long ^^ It's good to take a walk in Seongbukcheon in summer
